myn.addatude.protocol

Class LocationRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • myn.addatude.protocol.LocationRecord

  • public class LocationRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    LocationRecord is a class to store location information. It takes MessageInput and MessageOutput to decode and encode by using specific protocol specificaions. MessageInput and MessageOutput are mediators for inputstream and outputstream,
    Version:
    1.0
